title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 79-20.3 - Fees
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 79-20.3 - Fees

State Regulations
(a) Applicants
shall pay a fee of $50 for an initial license and a fee of $150 for the first
registration period. (b) Licensees
shall pay a fee of $150 for each triennial registration period. Notes
